<view class="page">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="hero-title">AI 正在分析</view>
    <view class="hero-subtitle">系统会识别训练中的姿态、节奏、稳定性和可能需要教练关注的风险点。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="row">
      <view>
        <view class="card-title">{{statusText}}</view>
        <view class="muted">{{task.progressText || '正在准备分析任务'}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="tag">{{task.progress || 0}}%</view>
    </view>
    <view class="progress-track" style="margin-top: 28rpx;">
      <view class="progress-bar" style="width: {{task.progress || 0}}%;"></view>
    </view>
    <view class="muted" style="margin-top: 22rpx;">可返回首页，任务状态会自动保留。体验版原型使用模拟分析流程。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="card" wx:if="{{task.status === 'failed'}}">
    <view class="card-title">分析失败</view>
    <view class="muted">请重新发起分析，如连续失败建议联系教练或客服。</view>
    <view class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 24rpx;" bindtap="retry">重新分析</view>
  </view>

  <view class="btn btn-ghost" style="margin-top: 28rpx;" bindtap="backHome">返回首页</view>
</view>

